{"tid":1541110,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"9月8 美領見","createTime":"2019-09-04T13:35:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T03:52:31.000Z","uid":210612,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f4d5bb65eb219472b63c4d5221993b5eaf4e9e0b","tid":1541110,"uid":210612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:35:39.000Z","msg":"<em>#這是一則文宣廣告#</em><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/MUPPkBeBkY55yqujZTayGQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FMUPPkBeBkY55yqujZTayGQ&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJPUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=8df437af\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/MUPPkBeBkY55yqujZTayGQ</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KzhOqUJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKzhOqUJ.jpg&h=2969a103&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>五大訴求缺一不可<br />\nFive Demands<br />\nNot One Less<br />\nLiberate Hong Kong<br />\nRevolution of Our Times</strong></span>"},{"pid":"725a15a135ff7e49fbb1367471d4252197d498d2","tid":1541110,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:35:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人 應承我！<br />\n一日未答應五大訴求 都要繼續上街</span></strong></span><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1ccda9de2dc2dabd9b761cd9e88b8a32dd36cc24","tid":1541110,"uid":267103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:37:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月8 兩點見！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"67b6426ffbcf8a5838ddfe496f00708bc99f43af","tid":1541110,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:37:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7631f53feeed305afddbdfa73099827ad8e960dd","tid":1541110,"uid":55384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:41:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"673b0c5b874fb017863e5bed53cce950c1a73b11","tid":1541110,"uid":83131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:50:03.000Z","msg":"推返行動Post上黎喇! 十點開窗嗌喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img